message:
Fix sideTrips schema mismatch + update page-generator README

- sideTrips: normalize_side_trip() unifies old format {destination,duration,highlights}
  to schema-compliant {name,date,role,description}
- Handles string array, old dict, and new dict input formats
- Updated page-generator/README.md to match current architecture

Add --json, --code-only, --compact output + Mintlify cleanup

Agent output improvements (5 of top 10 from cross-agent analysis):

#1 --json flag on all commands:
  - search: {type, query, results: [{rank, path, title, score, snippet}]}
  - show: {type, path, title, sections, content, code_blocks}
  - list: {type, categories: [{name, count}]} or {topics: [{path, title}]}
  - status: {type, last_sync, topics, categories, db_size_kb}
  - diff: {type, added, changed, removed, counts, up_to_date}
